'''夏琨塔拉·戴維'''（{{lang-kn|ಶಕುಂತಲಾ ದೇವಿ}}，拉丁轉寫：{{lang|en|Shakuntala Devi}}，又譯為'''萨昆塔拉·德维'''，{{bd|1929年|11月4日|2013年|4月21日|catIdx=Devi, Shakuntala}}），女性，生於[[印度|印度]][[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]，是[[神童|神童]]和著名{{Link-en|心算家|Mental calculator}}，有「人脑计算机」的美称。<ref name=HINDU>{{cite news |title=Shakuntala Devi strove to simplify maths for students |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/mathematical-genius-shakuntala-devi-no-more/article4640134.ece?homepage=true |newspaper=The Hindu |date=2013-04-21 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2016-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160218025606/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/mathematical-genius-shakuntala-devi-no-more/article4640134.ece?homepage=true |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=NYT>{{cite news |title=Shakuntala Devi, ‘Human Computer’ Who Bested the Machines, Dies at 83 |first=Haresh |last=Pandya |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/24/world/asia/shakuntala-devi-human-computer-dies-in-india-at-83.html |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2013-04-21 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106030934/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/04/24/world/asia/shakuntala-devi-human-computer-dies-in-india-at-83.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=TELEGRAPH>{{cite news |title=Obituary: Shakuntala Devi |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/10011281/Shakuntala-Devi.html |newspaper=The Telegraph |date=2013-04-22 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215001529/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/10011281/Shakuntala-Devi.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=JENSEN>{{cite journal |last=Jensen |first=Arthur R. |date=July–September 1990 |title=Speed of information processing in a calculating prodigy |journal=Intelligence |volume=14 |issue=3 |pages=259–274 |location=University of California, Berkeley, USA |url=http://stepanov.lk.net/mnemo/jensen.html |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104091345/http://stepanov.lk.net/mnemo/jensen.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=BBC>{{cite news |title=Obituary: India's 'human computer' Shakuntala Devi |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-india-22244118 |newspaper=BBC News |date=2013-04-22 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016110656/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-india-22244118 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 曾在28秒内心算出两个随机的13位数的乘积，并因这不可思议的计算能力而列入1982年版的《[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]》。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=NYT/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/>

雖然有報道將夏琨塔拉·戴維稱作「數學家」，但她'''並非'''真正意義上的數學家，<ref>{{cite journal|author=John Butcher|title=Hardy's taxi, <math>x^2+3y^2=p</math> and Michael Lennon|url=http://nzmathsoc.org.nz/downloads/newsletters/NZMSnews76_Aug1999.pdf|journal=The New Zealand Mathematical Society Newsletter|date=August 1999|number=76|pages=18-19|accessdate=2013-12-17|archive-date=2013-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505221528/http://nzmathsoc.org.nz/downloads/newsletters/NZMSnews76_Aug1999.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>因為研究數學和心算這兩種思維活動完全不同。

==生平==

夏琨塔拉·戴維出生在印度[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]市<ref name=NYT/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/>的一個正統[[康納達語|康納達語]]的[[婆羅門|婆羅門]]家庭。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=TIME>{{cite news |title=Science: Numbers Game |url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,822325,00.html |newspaper=Time |date=1952-07-14 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930140058/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,822325,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Math Genius and Guinness Record Holder Shakuntala Devi Passes Away at Age 83|author=IBTimes Staff Reporter|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/articles/459844/20130422/shakuntala-devi-mathematician-guinness-record-holder.htm|newspaper=International Business Times|date=2013-04-22|accessdate=2013-07-23|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104173919/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/articles/459844/20130422/shakuntala-devi-mathematician-guinness-record-holder.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她的父親因不願在廟中作一名祭司<ref name=TELEGRAPH/>，於是便加入了馬戲團作一名[[空中飛人|空中飛人]]、[[馴獸師|馴獸師]]、並表演[[走鋼絲|走鋼絲]]、變[[魔術|魔術]]。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=NYT/><ref name=BBC/><ref name=BANGALORE>{{cite news |title=She made learning maths as thrilling as magic |author1=Aditi Mishra |author2=Siddarth Kumar Jain |url=http://www.bangaloremirror.com/bangalore/others/She-made-learning-maths-as-thrilling-as-magic/articleshow/21204048.cms?&subsite= |newspaper=The Bangalore Mirror |date=2013-04-22 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108082049/http://www.bangaloremirror.com/bangalore/others/She-made-learning-maths-as-thrilling-as-magic/articleshow/21204048.cms?&subsite= |dead-url=no }}</ref> 當戴維約三歲時，她的父親就教她玩撲克牌的把戲，並發現她有熟記數字的能力。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=NYT/><ref name=BBC/> 於是她的父親就離開了馬戲團，帶她到路上表演快速且大量複雜的數字運算<ref name=NYT/>，而戴維在沒有接受任何相關的正規教育下竟也能做到。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/> 六歲時，戴維就在[[邁索爾|邁索爾]]大學展現了她驚人的運算及記憶能力。<ref name=NYT/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/>

1944年，戴維與其父親移居[[倫敦|倫敦]]。<ref name=YAHOO>{{cite news |title=India's math wizard, Shakuntala Devi |url=http://in.news.yahoo.com/india-s-math-wizard--shakuntala-devi-102612575.html |newspaper=Yahoo! India News |date=2013-04-22 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130502042455/http://in.news.yahoo.com/india-s-math-wizard--shakuntala-devi-102612575.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 到了1960年代中期，便回到了印度並嫁給一位[[加爾各答|加爾各答]]的行政服務官員Paritosh Bannerji<ref name=YAHOO/>，後於1979年離婚。<ref name=YAHOO/> 到了1980年代初期，戴維又回到了班加羅爾。<ref name=YAHOO/>

戴維曾到世界各地展示她的[[算術|算術]]天份，如1950年的[[歐洲|歐洲]]之旅、以及1976年在[[紐約|紐約]]的表演。<ref name=NYT/> 1988年，她再次到美國，並讓[[柏克萊加州大學|柏克萊加州大學]]的心理學教授{{Link-en|亞瑟·傑森|Arthur Jensen}}對她的能力進行研究。傑森在幾個任務中測試戴維的績效，其中包括了計算很大的數字。例如，計算61,629,875的立方根，以及170,859,375的七次方根。<ref name=TELEGRAPH/><ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite journal |last=Jensen |first=Arthur R. |date=July–September 1990 |title=Speed of information processing in a calculating prodigy |journal=Intelligence |volume=14 |issue=3 |pages=259–274 |location=University of California, Berkeley, USA |url=http://stepanov.lk.net/mnemo/jensen.html |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104091345/http://stepanov.lk.net/mnemo/jensen.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 傑森在其報告中說，在他還沒來得及把上述的數學問題記好在筆記本之前，戴維就已能夠給出解答了（以上的答案分別是395以及15）。<ref name=TELEGRAPH/><ref name=JENSEN/> 1990年，傑森將其發現發表在心理學的學術期刊《{{Link-en|智力（期刊）|Intelligence (journal)|智力}}》上。<ref name=TELEGRAPH/><ref name=JENSEN/>

除了作為一名心算家之外，戴維也是一名[[占星家|占星家]]並有多種著作，如食譜以及虛構小說。<ref name=NYT/><ref name=BBC/><ref name=BANGALORE/>

==成就==

* 1977年，戴維在美國與電腦同台競技，看誰先算出188,132,517的立方根，結果她贏了。同年，在[[南美以美大學|南美以美大學]]，她被要求計算一個201位數字的23次方根，並僅以50秒便得出了答案。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=JENSEN/> 她的答案「546,372,891」經由美國標準局Univac 1101電腦的計算得到了證實。為此，還有一套特別寫好了的程式以進行這樣龐大的運算。<ref>{{cite book |last=Smith |first=Steven Bradley |title=The Great Mental Calculators: The Psychology, Methods, and Lives of Calculating Prodigies, Past and Present |year=1983 |publisher=Columbia University Press|isbn=0231056400}}</ref>

* 1980年6月18日，戴維示範將兩個由[[倫敦帝國學院|倫敦帝國學院]]的計算機系所隨機選取的13位數字進行相乘（7,686,369,774,870 × 2,465,099,745,779），結果僅花28秒便得出了正確答案「18,947,668,177,995,426,462,773,730」。<ref name=NYT/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/> 這件事被記載在1982年的《[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]》之中。<ref name=NYT/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/>

==同性戀著作==
1977年她於印度發表了第一篇同性戀研究。<ref>{{Cite journal | title=Globalizing queer? AIDS, homophobia and the politics of sexual identity in India | author=Subir K Kole | journal=Globalization and Health | doi=10.1186/1744-8603-3-8 | date=2007-07-11 | url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2018684/ | pmid=17623106 | volume=3 | pages=8 | pmc=2018684 | access-date=2013-11-09 | archive-date=2022-01-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220128013216/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2018684/ | dead-url=no }}: "The first academic book on Indian homosexuals appeared in 1977 (The World of Homosexuals) written by Shakuntala Devi, the mathematics wizkid who was internationally known as the human computer. This book treated homosexuality in a positive light and reviewed socio-cultural and legal situation of homosexuality in India and contrasted that with the then gay liberation movement in USA."</ref> <ref name="worldoh">{{Cite book | title=The World of Homosexuals | author=Shakuntala Devi | publisher=Vikas Publishing House | year=1977 | isbn=9780706904789 | url=http://books.google.com/?id=PBwbAAAAYAAJ }}</ref> 在"For Straights Only"文獻中，她提到了她的興趣來源是由她嫁給了一個同性戀男性，因此渴望進一步研究同性戀來瞭解。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orinam.net/r-i-p-shakuntala-devi-math-evangelist-and-ally-of-the-queer-community/ |title=R.I.P. Shakuntala Devi, math-evangelist and ally of the queer community |access-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424195510/http://orinam.net/r-i-p-shakuntala-devi-math-evangelist-and-ally-of-the-queer-community/ |archive-date=2013-04-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==逝世==

2013年4月，戴維因呼吸系統問題而住進印度[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]的一家醫院，<ref name=HINDU/>兩周內併發心、腎臟病。<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=NYT/>2013年4月21日，戴維於醫院逝世<ref name=HINDU/><ref name=NYT/>，享年83歲<ref name=NYT/><ref name=TELEGRAPH/>，身後留有一女Anupama Banerji。<ref name=TELEGRAPH/><ref name=BANGALORE/>

==紀念==
2013年11月4日，Google在她的84歲冥誕當天，將Google首頁的[[Google商標|商標]]改為一個電子計算器及她的頭像以茲紀念<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.google.com/doodles/shakuntala-devis-84th-birthday |title=Shakuntala Devi's 84th Birthday |accessdate=2018-05-21 |archive-date=2018-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181104020949/https://www.google.com/doodles/shakuntala-devis-84th-birthday |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

